{"thag3.14:0.1":"Theragatha 3.14 ","thag3.14:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.14:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.14:0.4":"Gotamattheragatha ","thag3.14:1.1":"“Samsaram hi nirayam agacchissam, ","thag3.14:1.2":"Petalokamagamam punappunam; ","thag3.14:1.3":"Dukkhamamhipi tiracchanayoniyam, ","thag3.14:1.4":"Nekadha hi vusitam ciram maya. ","thag3.14:2.1":"Manusopi ca bhavobhiradhito, ","thag3.14:2.2":"Saggakayamagamam sakim sakim; ","thag3.14:2.3":"Rupadhatusu arupadhatusu, ","thag3.14:2.4":"Nevasannisu asannisutthitam. ","thag3.14:3.1":"Sambhava suvidita asaraka, ","thag3.14:3.2":"Sankhata pacalita saderita; ","thag3.14:3.3":"Tam viditva mahamattasambhavam, ","thag3.14:3.4":"Santimeva satima samajjhagan”ti. ","thag3.14:3.5":"… Gotamo thero …. "}